dct_title_s: The Large scale Liberty war map, indexed : an accurate and authentic compilation of the entire Western front with inset of Central Europe : particular features : battle lines, the twelve military sectors which make up the Western front, fortified cities, first and second class roads, canals, railroads, forts, forests and mountains, including separate index
dct_description_sm: Shows battle lines on July 1, 1916, and Dec. 1, 1917, and the farthest advance of the German armies, Sept. 1914.; Cover title.; Relief shown by shading.; Inset: Central Europe.
Scale approximately 1:633,600; 1 inch to 10 statute miles.
